+/*
+ * MetalSharp-owned native D3DMetal host ABI shim.
+ *
+ * Ports the behavior (not the branding) of CrossOver's D3DMetal host shim into
+ * MetalSharp Wine 11.5. CrossOver is only ever an oracle for behavior; this
+ * code is MetalSharp-owned. The exported `macdrv_functions` symbol and the
+ * `macdrv_functions_t` table layout (192 bytes, C_ASSERT-enforced) are Wine/DXMT
+ * ABI contract — the D3DMetal/DXMT payloads look them up by that exact name —
+ * so the name is retained deliberately; it is not CrossOver branding.
+ *
+ * Active backend selection uses MetalSharp-owned names (MS_ACTIVE_GRAPHICS_BACKEND
+ * = d3dmetal_native); no CX_/CrossOver identifiers appear in compiled output.
